{
  "slug": "multi-species-transmission-chains",
  "type": "html",
  "title": "Transmission Bridge Zones",
  "concept": "A pathogen moves from one population to another only when a third organism bridges the gap by feeding on both in sequence—risk maps to where feeding cycles overlap with all three populations.",
  "interactiveId": "14d06613-19a8-4876-8ada-3b56804e6ae2",
  "sourcePieceId": "51af7aa3-12c1-4e8d-9ac1-e9c627810490",
  "publishedAt": 1778496412605,
  "voiceScore": 0,
  "qualityFlag": "low",
  "content": {
    "type": "html",
    "html": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n<meta charset=\"utf-8\">\n<meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1\">\n<title>Transmission Bridge Zones</title>\n<style>\n  :root {\n    --bg: #faf7f1;\n    --fg: #1a1a1a;\n    --muted: #6b6b6b;\n    --line: #e5e0d6;\n    --reservoir: #c9a227;\n    --vector: #1a6b62;\n    --host: #8b4513;\n    --bridge: #d94a3d;\n  }\n  * { box-sizing: border-box; }\n  body {\n    font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, \"Segoe UI\", sans-serif;\n    margin: 0;\n    padding: 20px;\n    color: var(--fg);\n    background: var(--bg);\n    line-height: 1.5;\n  }\n  h2 {\n    font-size: 1.05rem;\n    font-weight: 600;\n    margin: 0 0 4px;\n  }\n  p.subhead {\n    margin: 0 0 20px;\n    color: var(--muted);\n    font-size: 0.9rem;\n  }\n  .controls {\n    display: flex;\n    flex-direction: column;\n    gap: 14px;\n    margin-bottom: 24px;\n  }\n  .control {\n    display: flex;\n    align-items: center;\n    gap: 12px;\n  }\n  .control label {\n    font-weight: 500;\n    min-width: 140px;\n    flex-shrink: 0;\n    font-size: 0.9rem;\n  }\n  .control input[type=range] {\n    flex: 1;\n    min-width: 100px;\n  }\n  .control output {\n    font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums;\n    font-weight: 600;\n    min-width: 4ch;\n    text-align: right;\n    font-size: 0.9rem;\n  }\n  #landscape {\n    width: 100%;\n    height: 300px;\n    border: 1px solid var(--line);\n    border-radius: 6px;\n    background: #fff;\n    position: relative;\n    overflow: hidden;\n    margin-bottom: 12px;\n  }\n  .zone {\n    position: absolute;\n    border-radius: 4px;\n    transition: all 240ms ease-out;\n    display: flex;\n    align-items: center;\n    justify-content: center;\n    font-size: 0.75rem;\n    font-weight: 600;\n    color: rgba(0,0,0,0.6);\n    text-align: center;\n    padding: 8px;\n  }\n  .bridge-indicator {\n    position: absolute;\n    width: 8px;\n    height: 8px;\n    border-radius: 50%;\n    background: var(--bridge);\n    transition: all 240ms ease-out;\n    z-index: 10;\n  }\n  .legend {\n    margin: 16px 0 8px;\n    display: flex;\n    flex-wrap: wrap;\n    gap: 16px;\n    font-size: 0.85rem;\n  }\n  .legend-item {\n    display: flex;\n    align-items: center;\n    gap: 6px;\n  }\n  .legend-box {\n    width: 16px;\n    height: 16px;\n    border-radius: 2px;\n  }\n  .reading {\n    margin: 18px 0 6px;\n    padding: 12px 14px;\n    background: #fff;\n    border: 1px solid var(--line);\n    border-radius: 6px;\n    font-size: 0.9rem;\n  }\n  .reading strong {\n    font-weight: 600;\n  }\n  p.caption {\n    margin: 14px 0 0;\n    color: var(--muted);\n    font-size: 0.875rem;\n  }\n  @media (max-width: 480px) {\n    .control {\n      flex-direction: column;\n      align-items: flex-start;\n      gap: 6px;\n    }\n    .control label {\n      min-width: 0;\n    }\n    .control input[type=range] {\n      width: 100%;\n    }\n    #landscape {\n      height: 260px;\n    }\n    .zone {\n      font-size: 0.65rem;\n      padding: 6px;\n    }\n  }\n</style>\n</head>\n<body>\n<h2>Adjust where populations live and where the bridge organism feeds</h2>\n<p class=\"subhead\">A pathogen passes from source to destination only when the carrier feeds on both.</p>\n\n<div class=\"controls\">\n  <div class=\"control\">\n    <label for=\"reservoir\">Source population:</label>\n    <input id=\"reservoir\" type=\"range\" min=\"0\" max=\"70\" value=\"10\" aria-describedby=\"reservoir-out\">\n    <output id=\"reservoir-out\" for=\"reservoir\">10%</output>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"control\">\n    <label for=\"bridge\">Carrier feeding zone:</label>\n    <input id=\"bridge\" type=\"range\" min=\"0\" max=\"70\" value=\"35\" aria-describedby=\"bridge-out\">\n    <output id=\"bridge-out\" for=\"bridge\">35%</output>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"control\">\n    <label for=\"host\">Destination population:</label>\n    <input id=\"host\" type=\"range\" min=\"30\" max=\"100\" value=\"70\" aria-describedby=\"host-out\">\n    <output id=\"host-out\" for=\"host\">70%</output>\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n<div id=\"landscape\" role=\"img\" aria-label=\"Landscape showing three horizontal zones representing populations and feeding ranges\"></div>\n\n<div class=\"legend\">\n  <div class=\"legend-item\">\n    <div class=\"legend-box\" style=\"background: var(--reservoir); opacity: 0.4;\"></div>\n    <span>Source</span>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"legend-item\">\n    <div class=\"legend-box\" style=\"background: var(--vector); opacity: 0.4;\"></div>\n    <span>Carrier feeds</span>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"legend-item\">\n    <div class=\"legend-box\" style=\"background: var(--host); opacity: 0.4;\"></div>\n    <span>Destination</span>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"legend-item\">\n    <div class=\"legend-box\" style=\"background: var(--bridge);\"></div>\n    <span>Bridge formed</span>\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"reading\">\n  Transmission possible: <strong id=\"transmission\">No</strong>.\n  Bridge status: <strong id=\"bridge-status\">Carrier doesn't reach both populations</strong>.\n</div>\n\n<p class=\"caption\" id=\"caption\">The carrier must feed in zones that overlap with both source and destination. Move the sliders to form or break the bridge.</p>\n\n<script>\n  (function () {\n    var reservoirSlider = document.getElementById('reservoir');\n    var bridgeSlider = document.getElementById('bridge');\n    var hostSlider = document.getElementById('host');\n    var reservoirOut = document.getElementById('reservoir-out');\n    var bridgeOut = document.getElementById('bridge-out');\n    var hostOut = document.getElementById('host-out');\n    var transmission = document.getElementById('transmission');\n    var bridgeStatus = document.getElementById('bridge-status');\n    var caption = document.getElementById('caption');\n    var landscape = document.getElementById('landscape');\n\n    var reservoirZone = document.createElement('div');\n    reservoirZone.className = 'zone';\n    reservoirZone.style.background = 'var(--reservoir)';\n    reservoirZone.style.opacity = '0.4';\n    reservoirZone.textContent = 'Source';\n    landscape.appendChild(reservoirZone);\n\n    var bridgeZone = document.createElement('div');\n    bridgeZone.className = 'zone';\n    bridgeZone.style.background = 'var(--vector)';\n    bridgeZone.style.opacity = '0.4';\n    bridgeZone.textContent = 'Carrier';\n    landscape.appendChild(bridgeZone);\n\n    var hostZone = document.createElement('div');\n    hostZone.className = 'zone';\n    hostZone.style.background = 'var(--host)';\n    hostZone.style.opacity = '0.4';\n    hostZone.textContent = 'Destination';\n    landscape.appendChild(hostZone);\n\n    var bridgeIndicator = document.createElement('div');\n    bridgeIndicator.className = 'bridge-indicator';\n    bridgeIndicator.style.opacity = '0';\n    landscape.appendChild(bridgeIndicator);\n\n    function update() {\n      var resStart = +reservoirSlider.value;\n      var bridgeStart = +bridgeSlider.value;\n      var hostStart = +hostSlider.value;\n\n      var resEnd = resStart + 25;\n      var bridgeEnd = bridgeStart + 30;\n      var hostEnd = Math.min(hostStart + 25, 100);\n\n      reservoirOut.textContent = resStart + '%';\n      bridgeOut.textContent = bridgeStart + '%';\n      hostOut.textContent = hostStart + '%';\n\n      reservoirZone.style.left = resStart + '%';\n      reservoirZone.style.width = '25%';\n      reservoirZone.style.top = '20px';\n      reservoirZone.style.height = '60px';\n\n      bridgeZone.style.left = bridgeStart + '%';\n      bridgeZone.style.width = '30%';\n      bridgeZone.style.top = '100px';\n      bridgeZone.style.height = '100px';\n\n      hostZone.style.left = hostStart + '%';\n      hostZone.style.width = '25%';\n      hostZone.style.top = '220px';\n      hostZone.style.height = '60px';\n\n      var reachesSource = (bridgeStart <= resEnd && bridgeEnd >= resStart);\n      var reachesDestination = (bridgeStart <= hostEnd && bridgeEnd >= hostStart);\n      var bridgeFormed = reachesSource && reachesDestination;\n\n      if (bridgeFormed) {\n        transmission.textContent = 'Yes';\n        bridgeStatus.textContent = 'Carrier feeds on both populations';\n        caption.textContent = 'The carrier picks up the pathogen from the source, then delivers it to the destination through feeding. The bridge is active.';\n        bridgeIndicator.style.opacity = '1';\n        bridgeIndicator.style.left = ((bridgeStart + bridgeEnd) / 2) + '%';\n        bridgeIndicator.style.top = '150px';\n      } else {\n        transmission.textContent = 'No';\n        bridgeIndicator.style.opacity = '0';\n        if (!reachesSource && !reachesDestination) {\n          bridgeStatus.textContent = 'Carrier feeds in the wrong area';\n          caption.textContent = 'The carrier doesn\\'t reach either population. No contact means no transmission path.';\n        } else if (!reachesSource) {\n          bridgeStatus.textContent = 'Carrier reaches destination but not source';\n          caption.textContent = 'The carrier feeds on the destination but never picks up the pathogen from the source. The bridge is broken.';\n        } else {\n          bridgeStatus.textContent = 'Carrier reaches source but not destination';\n          caption.textContent = 'The carrier picks up the pathogen from the source but never delivers it—doesn\\'t feed on the destination. The bridge is broken.';\n        }\n      }\n    }\n\n    reservoirSlider.addEventListener('input', update);\n    bridgeSlider.addEventListener('input', update);\n    hostSlider.addEventListener('input', update);\n\n    update();\n  })();\n</script>\n</body>\n</html>"
  }
}
